title.#text: Field test evaluation in Turkey trials: Results and best practice

oaf:result.description: - Motorcycle couriers: DynaHUBs will integrate with the scheduled and unscheduled delivery orders of motorcycle couriers in order feed into its core scheduling system. Later, integrating those with delivery orders from other sources, DynaHUBs will live update the courier delivery schedules. We will also mitigate the possible lack of systems to integrate at couriers. We anticipate some couriers not having scheduling systems, rather running at the operator level. - Groceries: We will seek to integrate (at least at the test level) the time-scheduled delivery orders in Groceries. - E-commerce vendors: Similar to Groceries, we will also integrate with e-commerce vendors. We may start with e-commerce vendors given their flexibility in delivery time-windows.
